1 23.1-07-06. Duties of the department.
2 The department shall:
3 1. Hold at least one examination each year, administered by the department or a third-
4 party examination service, at a designated time and place for the purpose of
5 examining candidates for certification.
6 2. Promote the program of certification of water supply and wastewater disposal system
7 operators.
8 3. Distribute notices and applications and to receive and evaluate applications.
9 4. Collect fees for initial certification and annual renewal.
10 5. Prepare, conduct, and grade examinations. The department may use a third-party
11 examination service to prepare, conduct, and grade examinations.
12 6. Maintain records of operator qualifications, certification examination results, and a
13 register of certified operators.
14 7. Promote and schedule regular training schools and programs.
15 8. Adopt rules necessary to carry out this chapter.
